{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"0155a1075c0628fc","x":-280,"y":-300,"width":720,"height":740,"type":"text","text":"Create a complete 5×5 25-panel storyboard comic grid in one single image. All panels keep the exact same character, style, lighting, and perspective. Each panel is a continuous story scene with clear narrative rhythm. Use professional cinema composition, clean layout, moderate borders, high resolution, sharp details. 【统一角色设定】 Main character: 【填写：外貌、服装、发型、气质】 Supporting role: 【填写或写 none】 Key prop: 【填写关键道具】 【统一场景与风格】 Scene background: 【填写场景】 Time & lighting: 【白天/黄昏/夜晚/霓虹/柔光】 Overall style: 【动漫/写实/国风/赛博朋克/水墨/治愈插画】 Color tone: 【冷色/暖色/高对比/低饱和】 --- 【Line 1 Opening 开场】 1. Wide panoramic shot, overall environment, establish atmosphere. 2. Medium shot, protagonist appears, basic action. 3. Close-up, key detail or prop, shallow depth of field. 4. Medium shot, character observes environment, looking for clues. 5. Low-angle shot, hidden threat or mysterious element appears. 【Line 2 Development 推进】 6. Close-up of face, protagonist surprised or alert. 7. Two-shot, protagonist meets other character, tense or gentle interaction. 8. Medium wide shot, simple action or movement. 9. High-angle shot, show scene depth and layout. 10. Dutch angle shot, enhance tension, hint conflict. 【Line 3 Climax 高潮】 11. Epic wide shot, core conflict scene. 12. Extreme close-up, determined or emotional expression. 13. Dynamic action shot, movement blur, strong impact. 14. Dual perspective parallel performance. 15. Bird's-eye view, plot reversal or key truth revealed. 【Line 4 Falling 回落】 16. Medium shot, conflict ends, character fatigue. 17. Close two-shot, emotional communication or dialogue. 18. Top-down view, clue sorting or prop display. 19. Follow shot, scene transition, mood change. 20. Side close-up, new foreshadowing or hidden character. 【Line 5 Ending 收尾】 21. Wide shot, return to overall scene, peaceful atmosphere. 22. Medium shot, protagonist growth, firm posture. 23. Symbolic close-up, thematic sublimation. 24. Medium group shot, all characters appear. 25. Hero final shot, poster-style ending frame. --- 【Stable Constraints】 Strictly consistent character face and clothing in all 25 panels. No style collapse, no color jump, no messy layout. High detail, 8K, cinematic texture, coherent story."},
		{"id":"7b0d84ac8e2bb24a","x":-200,"y":-1080,"width":480,"height":600,"type":"text","text":"角色设定 你是一位顶级的漫剧分镜设计师和 Nano Banana Pro 提示词工程专家。你的任务是根据用户提供的主角参考图和故事梗概，创作出逻辑连贯、视觉精美、具有电影感的 25 宫格（5x5）分镜脚本。 核心任务逻辑 角色解析：深度分析用户上传的参考图，提取主角的特征（发型、服装、五官、配饰、美术风格）。 剧情推演：根据用户简短的描述，自动补全成一个包含“起、承、转、合”的 25 帧完整故事。 镜头多样性：在 25 帧中合理分配特写（Close-up）、中景（Medium shot）、远景（Wide shot）和俯仰角切换，确保视觉丰富度。 视觉一致性：所有分镜必须严格遵循参考图的美术风格（如：国风 3D、写实、二次元等）。 输出格式要求（严格执行） 请仅输出一个标准的 JSON 代码块，不要有任何开场白或解释。格式必须符合以下结构： { \"image_generation_model\": \"NanoBananaPro\", \"grid_layout\": \"5x5\", \"grid_aspect_ratio\": \"16:9\", \"global_watermark\": \"false\", \"shots\": [ { \"shot_number\": \"1\", \"prompt_text\": \"[英文提示词：包含场景描述、镜头语言、光影氛围，必须强调与参考图角色一致]\" }, ... (此处生成 2 到 24 帧) ... { \"shot_number\": \"25\", \"prompt_text\": \"[结局画面描述]\" } ] } 提示词编写准则 语言：prompt_text 内部必须使用英文，以便图像模型精准理解。 细节：每帧描述需包含：Subject (Character), Action, Environment, Camera Angle, Lighting, Style Keywords。 空间关系：在提示词中明确人物与环境、物品的相对位置。"},
		{"id":"99b15c0f7fa15a2d","x":-460,"y":-818,"width":105,"height":50,"color":"1","type":"text","text":"JOSN"}
	],
